        "installation": "<p>Nosso processo de instala\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e9 simples e bem detalhado:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/docs.pagar.me\/docs\/woocommerce-introdu%C3%A7%C3%A3o\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Vis\u00e3o geral sobre nosso plugin<\/a>;<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/docs.pagar.me\/docs\/requisitos-de-instala%C3%A7%C3%A3o-woocommerce\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Requisitos de Instala\u00e7\u00e3o<\/a>;<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/docs.pagar.me\/docs\/instalando-o-plugin-woocommerce-1\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Instalando o plugin<\/a>;<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/docs.pagar.me\/docs\/configurando-os-meios-de-pagamento-woocommerce\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Configurando os meios de pagamento<\/a>;<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/docs.pagar.me\/docs\/configurando-a-dashboard-woocommerce\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Configurando a dashboard<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "changelog": "<p>Lan\u00e7amos vers\u00f5es regularmente com melhorias, corre\u00e7\u00f5es e atualiza\u00e7\u00f5es.<\/p>\n<h4>3.2.1 (30\/01\/2024)<\/h4>\n<p>Voc\u00ea pode conferir essas atualiza\u00e7\u00f5es aqui: <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/pagarme\/woocommerce\/releases\/tag\/3.2.1\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Github<\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Corre\u00e7\u00f5es:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Parcelamento de cart\u00e3o de cr\u00e9dito<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.2.0 (29\/01\/2024)<\/h4>\n<p>Voc\u00ea pode conferir essas atualiza\u00e7\u00f5es aqui: <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/pagarme\/woocommerce\/releases\/tag\/3.2.0\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Github<\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Novas implementa\u00e7\u00f5es:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Autonomia na escolha dos m\u00e9todos de pagamento para Subscriptions <\/li>\n<li>Parcelamento em at\u00e9 12x no cart\u00e3o de cr\u00e9dito para Subscriptions<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Corre\u00e7\u00f5es:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Erro ao acessar a p\u00e1gina de edi\u00e7\u00e3o de produtos<\/li>\n<li>Compatibiliza\u00e7\u00e3o com PHP 8.2\/8.3<\/li>\n<li>Erro ao finalizar compra de custo 0<\/li>\n<li>Campos primeiro nome e sobrenome n\u00e3o obrigat\u00f3rios<\/li>\n<li>Falha ao gerar o pedido recorrente por falta de CustomerId<\/li>\n<li>Redu\u00e7\u00e3o duplicada de estoque &#8211; @tiagopapile<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "description": "<p>Desenvolvemos um m\u00f3dulo que integra o Woocomerce a Pagar.me de forma pr\u00e1tica e segura, assim n\u00e3o \u00e9 preciso que seu time de tecnologia desenvolva nenhuma linha de c\u00f3digo. Basta instalar e configurar o m\u00f3dulo para usar!<\/p>\n",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Plugin cheio de erro<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jkaiomaciel\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9eee080faf58d2cba33daacb8e9caab0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9eee080faf58d2cba33daacb8e9caab0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jkaiomaciel\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jkaiomaciel<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 10, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Impossivel utilizar o sandbox, plugin cheio de erro, equipe deles informa que \u00e9 melhor fazer logo em produ\u00e7\u00e3o, como \u00e9 que vou migrar de vers\u00e3o e botar direto em produ\u00e7\u00e3o sem testar nada.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\"><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Cr\u00edtico Uncaught TypeError: Argument 1 passed to Pagarme\\Core\\Payment\\Aggregates\\Order::addPayment() must be an instance of Pagarme\\Core\\Payment\\Aggregates\\Payments\\AbstractPayment, null given, called in \/var\/www\/html\/wp-content\/plugins\/pagarme-payments-for-woocommerce\/vendor\/pagarme\/ecommerce-module-core\/src\/Kernel\/Services\/OrderService.php on line 378 and defined in \/var\/www\/html\/wp-content\/plugins\/pagarme-payments-for-woocommerce\/vendor\/pagarme\/ecommerce-module-core\/src\/Payment\/Aggregates\/Order.php:119 CONTEXT: {\"error\":{\"type\":1,\"file\":\"\\\/var\\\/www\\\/html\\\/wp-content\\\/plugins\\\/pagarme-payments-for-woocommerce\\\/vendor\\\/pagarme\\\/ecommerce-module-core\\\/src\\\/Payment\\\/Aggregates\\\/Order.php\",\"line\":119},\"backtrace\":[\"\",\"#0 \\\/var\\\/www\\\/html\\\/wp-content\\\/plugins\\\/pagarme-payments-for-woocommerce\\\/vendor\\\/pagarme\\\/ecommerce-module-core\\\/src\\\/Kernel\\\/Services\\\/OrderService.php(378): Pagarme\\Core\\Payment\\Aggregates\\Order-&gt;addPayment(NULL)\",\"#1 \\\/var\\\/www\\\/html\\\/wp-content\\\/plugins\\\/pagarme-payments-for-woocommerce\\\/vendor\\\/pagarme\\\/ecommerce-module-core\\\/src\\\/Kernel\\\/Services\\\/OrderService.php(259): Pagarme\\Core\\Kernel\\Services\\OrderService-&gt;extractPaymentOrderFromPlatformOrder(Object(Woocommerce\\Pagarme\\Concrete\\WoocommercePlatformOrderDecorator))\",\"#2\"]}<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Ruim demais<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/leodefaveri\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/f993183987bf4e3966a11c701fa71baf?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/f993183987bf4e3966a11c701fa71baf?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/leodefaveri\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">leodefaveri<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 16, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Vcs criaram um plugin que chamam de \"m\u00f3dulo\". Horr\u00edvel! N\u00e3o atoa, tem muito mais avalia\u00e7\u00e3o negativa que positiva. Que saudade de quando a gente buscava um plugin no reposit\u00f3rio e tava l\u00e1 o nome do Claudio como dev.  <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">E o que mais me deixa intrigado \u00e9 que vcs ganham com a venda, ou seja, por que fazer isso? Agora a vers\u00e3o antiga n\u00e3o funciona mais porque n\u00e3o muda o status, provavelmente bloquearam a algo e ficamos sem nada. O meu sincero pedido \u00e9: voltem com o plugin do Claudio e abandonem esse tro\u00e7o cheio de remendo feito por pessoas que n\u00e3o tem conhecimento. Daqui a pouco ningu\u00e9m mais no Woo vai usar pagarme. Nos grupos eu s\u00f3 vejo gente saindo e trocando de gateway, e pelo visto seremos os pr\u00f3ximos! E pra concluir, j\u00e1 sei que v\u00e3o falar pra entrar em contato com suporte, mas n\u00e3o d\u00e1 n\u00e3o, suporte zero!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Plugins com erros e n\u00e3o segue a diretrizes do Woocommerce<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/gabrielfilippi\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/8b9dfd0c7e27d98d6a3f3d04d4d5ea61?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/8b9dfd0c7e27d98d6a3f3d04d4d5ea61?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/gabrielfilippi\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gabrielfilippi<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 12, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Plugin cheio de erros, atribui\u00e7\u00e3o de status errados e n\u00e3o h\u00e1 uma devolutiva do time de desenvolvimento.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Ao entrar em contato com o suporte da Pagar.me pelo dashboard s\u00f3 agradecem o feedback, mas parece que pela quantidade de reclama\u00e7\u00f5es, n\u00e3o parecem estar preucupados com isso.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Um verdadeiro LIXO<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/lifprime\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/126bd344b64935937fbb8994036e62f4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/126bd344b64935937fbb8994036e62f4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/lifprime\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pres <small>(lifprime)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 28, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Engra\u00e7ado, tiraram uma solu\u00e7\u00e3o que funcionava perfeitamente bem pra colocar uma bosta de plugin que \u00e9 imposs\u00edvel de integrar. <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">O bot\u00e3o da integra\u00e7\u00e3o nas configura\u00e7\u00f5es do plugin tem um link especifico para a autorizar a integra\u00e7\u00e3o.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Porem ao clicar na bosta do bot\u00e3o voc\u00ea \u00e9 redirecionado 5x e n\u00e3o cai na tela de autoriza\u00e7\u00e3o para integrar, e n\u00e3o existe op\u00e7\u00e3o para fazer nada manualmente.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">1. hub.pagar.me\/apps\/ (link do bot\u00e3o com todas as chaves e credenciais, n\u00e3o vou coloca-lo completo aqui)<br \/>2. profile.mundipagg.com\/<br \/>3. id.pagar.me<br \/>4. dash.pagar.me<br \/>5. dash.pagar.me\/enterprises<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Olha o tamanho da incompet\u00eancia e da bagun\u00e7a dos \"desenvolvedores\" se \u00e9 que podem ser chamados assim, isso ai ta mais \u00e9 pra gambiarra de desenvolvedores juniors fazendo um remendo por cima do outro...<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/ol>\n<!-- \/wp:list --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">N\u00e3o consigo realizar a integra\u00e7\u00e3o<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/fneto\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/c31f1465d9f1daf2d248dac363d41a8f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/c31f1465d9f1daf2d248dac363d41a8f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/fneto\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">fneto<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 13, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Fiz os passos sugerido pela pr\u00f3pria plataforma, mas sou redirecionado para a p\u00e1gina inicial do dashboard ao clicar no bot\u00e3o de integrar <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Boa solu\u00e7\u00e3o mas incompleta<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/rafaelzrt\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/70d994a5e1ec6cad5a3021d92948ec7f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/70d994a5e1ec6cad5a3021d92948ec7f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/rafaelzrt\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rafaelzrt<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 8, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Boa solu\u00e7\u00e3o, funciona bem para a maioria dos casos simples por\u00e9m \u00e9 incompleta ainda para casos espec\u00edficos.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">N\u00e3o h\u00e1 uma solu\u00e7\u00e3o para Split de Pagamentos.<br \/><br \/>\u00c9 muito bom ter uma solu\u00e7\u00e3o desenvolvida pela pr\u00f3pria empresa. Traz estabilidade para a aplica\u00e7\u00e3o se quisermos utilizar esta ferramenta para pagamentos. Espero que melhorem para atender todos os casos poss\u00edveis.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Atendimento de suporte t\u00e9cnico da Pagar.me \u00e9 meio demorado. Atendimento de vendas poderia ser melhor informado, me passaram informa\u00e7\u00f5es erradas.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Amador e cobra R$ 0,10 por opea\u00e7\u00e3o<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/johnpaes\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/a24a67d98aef14f92e05602d12d90a3e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/a24a67d98aef14f92e05602d12d90a3e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/johnpaes\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">johnpaes<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 6, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">O plugin PagarMe tenta ser pr\u00e1tico na configura\u00e7\u00e3o e integra\u00e7\u00e3o, mas complica mais do que ajuda.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>N\u00e3o segue as regras de status do Woocommerce, muda para conclu\u00eddo o status processando, para os itens virtuais. Falei com os \u201ct\u00e9cnicos\u201d deles, mas fingem n\u00e3o entender esta regra b\u00e1sica.<\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>A id\u00e9ia do HUB para facilitar apenas retira autonomia de configura\u00e7\u00e3o.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>O plugin n\u00e3o captura os valores dos itens agregados do woocommerce, chegando um valor de cobran\u00e7a e outro para o pedido. Imagina que um pedido de 100 reais mostra 0,01 no pedido e 100 na cobran\u00e7a, l\u00e1 no painel do PagarMe.<\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>O plugin anterior funcionava perfeitamente, sem falhas. N\u00e3o sei porque n\u00e3o inclu\u00edram o PIX no plugin para atualizar. Lan\u00e7aram um novo infinitamente pior, que n\u00e3o funciona.<\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/ol>\n<!-- \/wp:list --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Plugin ruim e atendimento p\u00e9ssimo.<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/sallet\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/f8da55a3c0aee7bc753f93680b62f181?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/f8da55a3c0aee7bc753f93680b62f181?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/sallet\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sallet<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 19, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">O plugin do Claudio que foi criado no cret\u00e1cio funcionava lindamente. <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Sem chances usar este \"m\u00f3dulo\" para integrar no \"hub\". Se j\u00e1 come\u00e7ou desse jeito imagina quanta dor de cabe\u00e7a vai dai ainda. Hora de procurar alternativas.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Ruim demais bicho!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/laserstore\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/08580cd22e317aab76c6652709233c96?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/08580cd22e317aab76c6652709233c96?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/laserstore\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">laserstore<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 15, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Po, os caras est\u00e3o obrigando a migrar pra esse plugin burocr\u00e1tico \"por quest\u00f5es de seguran\u00e7a\". Primeiro que os caras chamam de \"m\u00f3dulo\" e no wordpress\/woocommerce sabemos que s\u00e3o \"plugins\". M\u00f3dulo \u00e9 nomenclatura pra Magento. Da\u00ed pode ser que os devs n\u00e3o estejam ambientados com nossa plataforma. Mas o pior \u00e9 que n\u00e3o consigo integrar, porque fica uma notifica\u00e7\u00e3o de que preciso adicionar o dom\u00ednio na plataforma e o link leva a uma p\u00e1gina em branco. \u00c9 at\u00e9 poss\u00edvel que n\u00e3o seja culpa do plugin, mas tem que ser uma coisa \"p\u00e1-pum\", integra\u00e7\u00e3o r\u00e1pida, a loja t\u00e1 rodando. Troquei versionamento da API e nada. Gente, nenhum gateway \u00e9 assim. Colocou a API, j\u00e1 era! T\u00e1 recebendo na loja! <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Voc\u00eas v\u00e3o me desculpar, sei que d\u00e1 um grande trabalho criar uma integra\u00e7\u00e3o dessas e eu odeio ficar aqui criticando ou avaliando mal, mas n\u00e3o tem nem compara\u00e7\u00e3o com o plugin do Cl\u00e1udio de trocentos anos atr\u00e1s mesmo sem atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o. Uma pena de verdade ter que migrar pra essa vers\u00e3o horr\u00edvel. \u00c9 de se pensar at\u00e9 em trocar de gateway. E s\u00f3 separaram os meios de pagamento porque um caminh\u00e3o de gente reclamou. Voc\u00ea precisam olhar o Woocomerce de forma um pouco diferente de plataformas prontas. A base de tudo aqui \u00e9 facilidade e personaliza\u00e7\u00e3o. Se vcs n\u00e3o podem oferecer isso, n\u00e3o estar\u00e3o alinhados ao que n\u00f3s, lojistas e desenvolvedores queremos!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Melhorou muito!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/andreabe\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/ec1508ebe792d8e9d4b230b12bf45ede?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/ec1508ebe792d8e9d4b230b12bf45ede?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/andreabe\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">andreabe<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 14, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">A nova vers\u00e3o funciona muito bem! Tive alguns problemas no sandbox para a valida\u00e7\u00e3o de pagamentos de pix e boleto.  Foi preciso acionar o suporte do pagar.me (muito prestativo, por sinal) para validarem manualmente.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Al\u00e9m disso h\u00e1 alguns pontos para melhorar, mas nada que n\u00e3o d\u00ea para resolver com pequenos ajustes no c\u00f3digo. Por exemplo:<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Aba 'carteira' fica vis\u00edvel e acess\u00edvel na p\u00e1gina de perfil do cliente mesmo quando a op\u00e7\u00e3o de armazenar dados de cart\u00e3o est\u00e1 desativada<\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Estilo das p\u00e1ginas de comprova\u00e7\u00e3o de pagamento <\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/ul>\n<!-- \/wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Continuem assim!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
    },
